column5: Did pretty well in a short period of time between my nephew, brother, and myself.  Caught six fish including my brothers 31 inch pike right off the bat.  I managed to land a couple of 18 inch largies, but the highlight was this bass that my nephew landed.  It was his PB of 16 inches.  Jumped twice to add a little excitement.  He set the hook, fought it, and released it all by himself.  Not bad for a 10 year old.
Yup that's my boy!!!  Thanks for posting.
Love it,that's really what it's all about !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!.Not a bad day yourselves for a short time either !
